events.name: DePaul Blue Demons at Marquette Golden Eagles

headlines.description: — The only suspenseful part of Marquette’s blowout victory over slumping DePaul was whether Tyler Kolek would remain on the floor long enough to break the Golden Eagles’ 29-year-old game assists record.
headlines.shortLinkText: Tyler Kolek has school-record 18 assists to help No. 7 Marquette rout DePaul, 105-71

events.name: Duke Blue Devils at Miami Hurricanes

headlines.description: — Jeremy Roach scored 16 points to lead No. 8 Duke to an 84-55 victory over Miami on Wednesday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Jeremy Roach leads No. 8 Duke in 84-55 rout over Miami

events.name: Illinois Fighting Illini at Penn State Nittany Lions

headlines.description: — While Penn State’s Bryce Jordan Center might hold three times as many fans as the program’s rickety old Rec Hall, the nearly 100-year-old facility was at its atmospheric best Wednesday night — at No. 12 Illinois' expense.
headlines.shortLinkText: Zach Hicks makes 3 free throws with 3 seconds left to lift Penn State past No. 12 Illinois, 90-89
